short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Scooby profiler lets you debug backend queries for different http requests.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Scooby profiler is a chrome extension to debug backend queries for different HTTP requests. This lets you profile your views too. You need to install django-scooby-profiler package to make it work with Django.
